    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Be quick__ to an-tic--i-pate__ our foes___ ere we be en--slaved__ by them__ that blas-pheme__ Thee and__ that men---ace us____ with__ their___ threats, O mer-ci-ful Christ___ our God; by___ Thy Cross__ de-feat them___ that op--pose__ us__ that they___ may know___ how might--y is the____ faith of__ Or--tho-dox__ Chris-----tians, through Thy pure Moth--er’s prayers for us__ all, O on-ly___ Friend of__ man.__"
